Tianjin Zhonghuan to Invest 2.3 Billion Yuan in Solar Unit

-- B y   B a l d a v e   S i n g h
-- 
2011-08-15T03:20:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-15/tianjin-zhonghuan-to-invest-2-3-billion-yuan-in-solar-unit.html
Tianjin Zhonghuan Semiconductor
Joint-Stock Co. plans to invest an additional 2.3 billion yuan
in its Inner Mongolia Zhonghuan Photovoltaic Material Co. unit
to expand silicon and wafer production capacity, according to a
filing to the Shenzhen stock exchange today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Baldave Singh at 
 bsingh35@bloomberg.net  